image_analysis.description: A photograph of the interior of a closet. The closet contains a top shelf with folded white towels, a metal hanging rod with various items of clothing including white robes, patterned robes (one black/gold, one purple/maroon), and a pair of grey patterned trousers. Several empty wooden hangers are visible on the right side of the rod. The walls are a light beige/yellow color.
